Description:

This is a small project for auto-download and filter
specific contents from 1)hkbisi.com and 2)SexInSex.

In fact, this project only care about the subtile threads.
It will simply ignore all other unnecessary information. In
other words, it's a content extraction program using
human-made-filter(I made it!!).

The logic of this project is quite simple. No need to
explain here. Just look at the original source files and
that would be enough.
